/Tm { _tm astore pop iTm 0 0 moveto } bd
/ux 0.0 def
/uy 0.0 def
/F {
  /Tp exch def
  /Tf exch def
  Tf findfont Tp scalefont setfont
  /cf Tf def  /cs Tp def
